page.title: 09HOBBIES
page.content:
My hobbies are football and reading.
{FOOTBALL I am not very good at this but I like playing it a lot.I am training for a football team this season called the Westminster Colts Under 13 team.I have got three trophies and one shield.I received these when playing for a team called Co-op Imps Under 12 team.They were a very good team and got through to two finals but we lost one of them.
{READING I enjoy reading a lot and I am good at it.My reading age is 12.5 and I am only 11 years old.At home I have 67 comics and 8 annuals.
